OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Frain spreads eastwards over Orkney
OL,7,Fthis evening, dry and cloudy for
OL,8,FShetland. Overnight, rain spreads into
OL,9,FShetland and becomes heavy. Strong
OL,10,Fsoutheasterly winds and risk of gales.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,13,Frain clearing to the east. Showers in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon with some bright or
OL,15,Fsunny spells. Strong southeasterly
OL,16,Fwinds becoming westerly, gales
OL,17,Fpossible in the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
