OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,6,Fand bright spells most of Saturday,
OL,7,Fthen rain and strong winds overnight
OL,8,Finto Sunday. Rain, sleet, and strong
OL,9,Fwinds clearing to blustery showers
OL,10,FSunday. Dry with sunny spells Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
